title: I am hardstuck Iron,  AMA + Talk league things with an Iron Brony
body: Ask me anything,  league related or not.  Willing to discuss League related things a little more,  rather than just the Q + A format .  Ask me something I might not understand yet,  i'll give you my understanding and we can cross reference!  Coaches and know it alls welcome.  Oh,  and Tips welcome too,  this is a generalish thread so I don't have to post too many :D
